WEBVTT

00:00:00.349 --> 00:00:01.777
numer finf.

00:00:02.526 --> 00:00:06.452
 mir hobn gehaltn in redn vegn BYDGOSZCZ.

00:00:05.952 --> 00:00:06.908
yo.

00:00:06.677 --> 00:00:10.113
zogt mir, vu gefint zikh genoy BYDGOSZCZ?

00:00:10.643 --> 00:00:13.373
vu g- vu er gefint zikh? dos iz a

00:00:13.373 --> 00:00:15.277
dos a provints shtot

00:00:17.022 --> 00:00:19.260
in dem gegnt fun Toyrn

00:00:19.907 --> 00:00:21.555
WROCLAWEK

00:00:23.282 --> 00:00:25.025
dos iz klenere shtetlekh.

00:00:25.025 --> 00:00:27.574
dos di, di, di hoypt provints shtot.

00:00:27.574 --> 00:00:28.659
BYDGOSZCZ.

00:00:28.767 --> 00:00:30.431
oyf POMMERN take.

00:00:30.943 --> 00:00:32.742
es iz bay der grenets?

00:00:32.833 --> 00:00:36.163
neyn, UNK tsu di grenets, PANI, nokh a hipsh shtikl

00:00:36.163 --> 00:00:37.164
vegs.

00:00:37.963 --> 00:00:38.750
yo.

00:00:38.402 --> 00:00:40.778
dort iz do a taykh a barimter

00:00:40.778 --> 00:00:42.614
vos heyst BRDA.

00:00:43.988 --> 00:00:47.933
der, der taykh hot, hot, hot er gehat zeyer a sheynem

00:00:47.933 --> 00:00:49.112
kanal.

00:00:49.253 --> 00:00:51.356
er iz geven zeyer populer.

00:00:52.054 --> 00:00:53.043
BRDA.

00:00:53.218 --> 00:00:55.119
me ken vayter geyn?

00:00:55.210 --> 00:00:58.252
haklal, shelt dikh for az der SIENKIEWICZ

00:00:58.252 --> 00:01:00.721
tsu velekhn ikh hob zikh dortn gevondn

00:01:00.812 --> 00:01:02.645
iz gevezn a Minsker

00:01:03.023 --> 00:01:04.772
fun Minsk Mazovyetsk.

00:01:05.081 --> 00:01:08.484
er hot mikh nisht gekent. ikh hob im oykh nisht gekent

00:01:08.828 --> 00:01:12.771
ober m'hot zikh tsunoyfgeredt, PANI, az me ken Minsker a sakh

00:01:14.042 --> 00:01:15.808
un er hot mikh geratn

00:01:16.202 --> 00:01:18.266
az ikh zol zikh ibershpatsirn

00:01:18.266 --> 00:01:21.292
in VOYEVODISHn komitet fun di parteyen.

00:01:21.315 --> 00:01:23.097
iz do a pulkovnik

00:01:23.340 --> 00:01:24.616
⟨ALSTER⟩

00:01:25.348 --> 00:01:28.661
er iz geven, er iz geven der got, PANI

00:01:28.661 --> 00:01:31.096
fun yene p- gantse provints.

00:01:31.913 --> 00:01:34.674
"un dertseyl im az bist gevezn bay mir

00:01:35.001 --> 00:01:39.045
un zog im az du voltst gevolt," PANI, "zikh basheftikn," PANI

00:01:39.405 --> 00:01:41.171
"un e- er vet dikh erleydikn."

00:01:41.532 --> 00:01:43.416
nu, ikh hob azoy getun

00:01:43.641 --> 00:01:46.824
un m'hot zikh a bisl funandergeshmuest. er iz geven a yid

00:01:47.033 --> 00:01:48.326
der ⟨ALSTER⟩

00:01:49.480 --> 00:01:52.511
un dafke gehat a tipishn yidishn oyszen

00:01:53.209 --> 00:01:57.050
ober er iz gevezn an amoliker knaker, PANI, in di partey

00:01:57.445 --> 00:01:59.346
iz er aroysgeshvumen

00:02:00.145 --> 00:02:01.607
un

00:02:01.613 --> 00:02:05.061
er hot gegebn zayn haskome az er vet erleydikn

00:02:05.061 --> 00:02:06.520
un ikh hob im gegebn d-

00:02:06.520 --> 00:02:09.588
dates mayne, ver un ven, fun vanet, fun vos

00:02:09.696 --> 00:02:12.021
in velekher eynheyt ikh bin, un er hot ar-

00:02:12.021 --> 00:02:12.705
un

00:02:12.705 --> 00:02:16.507
un ikh bin shoyn UNK in militer tsurik nisht gegangen.

00:02:16.513 --> 00:02:18.886
ikh bin shoyn geblibn dortn bay dem

00:02:19.062 --> 00:02:20.861
bay dem SIENKIEWICZn

00:02:22.302 --> 00:02:24.540
getrogn hob ikh dem mundir

00:02:25.356 --> 00:02:28.036
vayl dos hot tsugegebn a bisl mer, PANI

00:02:28.036 --> 00:02:29.264
khshives

00:02:32.038 --> 00:02:35.637
un faktish, emes geredt, hot zikh bay mir

00:02:35.637 --> 00:02:37.081
dortn di milkhome

00:02:37.081 --> 00:02:38.124
geendikt.

00:02:38.367 --> 00:02:40.152
di milkhome hot nokh gedoyert

00:02:40.152 --> 00:02:42.529
hot nokh gedoyert a knap yor tsayt

00:02:43.446 --> 00:02:44.891
a yor nisht

00:02:45.336 --> 00:02:48.151
ober a por, sheyne por khadoshim

00:02:48.151 --> 00:02:48.960
⟨az⟩

00:02:48.171 --> 00:02:49.819
in velkhe date UNK

00:02:48.960 --> 00:02:51.441
a dray, a dray fir khadoshim.

00:02:51.276 --> 00:02:52.380
un itst

00:02:51.441 --> 00:02:53.095
ikh bin fun onfang

00:02:53.095 --> 00:02:54.898
fun onfang

00:02:56.057 --> 00:02:57.128
FEBRERO

00:02:57.128 --> 00:02:58.714
aroys fun shpitol

00:02:58.714 --> 00:03:01.749
un di milkhome hot zikh geendikt in onfang fun MAYO.

00:03:03.358 --> 00:03:07.520
un ikh bin gevorn der hoypt dortn fun propagande in dem amt.

00:03:07.611 --> 00:03:08.949
dos iz gevezn

00:03:08.949 --> 00:03:10.198
a amt vos

00:03:10.198 --> 00:03:12.245
vos hot unterligt, PANI

00:03:12.572 --> 00:03:15.345
bay etlekhene un tsvontsik shtetlekh

00:03:15.345 --> 00:03:18.070
vos zenen arayngegangen in dem provints arayn

00:03:18.070 --> 00:03:21.860
un m'hot badarft shafn dortn azelekhe enlekhe pletser

00:03:21.860 --> 00:03:24.210
opzukhn mentshn pasike

00:03:24.210 --> 00:03:25.762
avekshteln zikh

00:03:26.241 --> 00:03:29.137
o- un onheybn, PANI, tsu farpoylishn

00:03:30.561 --> 00:03:31.938
in dem shetekh.

00:03:32.860 --> 00:03:34.503
un

00:03:35.269 --> 00:03:38.570
un ikh hob zikh dortn gants gut oysgetoygt, PANI

00:03:38.695 --> 00:03:40.984
geven a sheyner plats

00:03:41.057 --> 00:03:42.198
oyf dem

00:03:42.272 --> 00:03:44.460
in dem, ⟨oyf⟩ dem BYDGOSZCZ

00:03:45.377 --> 00:03:48.183
hob ikh avekgeshtelt a rizedike mape

00:03:48.183 --> 00:03:50.048
hot geheysn makhn spetsyeln

00:03:50.048 --> 00:03:51.311
a mape

00:03:51.503 --> 00:03:52.816
a hiltserne

00:03:52.816 --> 00:03:54.129
un ale tog

00:03:54.321 --> 00:03:55.997
i- fleg ikh makhn

00:03:55.997 --> 00:03:58.089
n- dem front linye

00:03:58.089 --> 00:03:59.714
vi zi rukt zikh iber

00:03:59.822 --> 00:04:01.574
a mape fun Poyln

00:04:01.574 --> 00:04:02.789
un Daytshland

00:04:02.789 --> 00:04:03.928
un Rusland

00:04:03.928 --> 00:04:06.161
vos g- vos hot ilustrirt

00:04:06.319 --> 00:04:08.856
vu, vu gefint zikh der front

00:04:08.856 --> 00:04:11.176
vayl ale tog hot men bafrayt an ander

00:04:11.176 --> 00:04:13.960
an andere shtot, an andern shetekh, PANI

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:16.860
un s'iz geven fil mentshn zenen geganen kukn dortn

00:04:16.983 --> 00:04:18.259
me zol zen.

00:04:18.199 --> 00:04:21.905
zogt mir, ir hot gezogt az

00:04:22.198 --> 00:04:25.789
men hot gedarft farpoylishn dem shetekh.

00:04:25.789 --> 00:04:28.638
ir kent derklern vos heyst farpoylishn?

00:04:28.273 --> 00:04:30.207
vayl er iz geven fardaytsht.

00:04:30.501 --> 00:04:33.229
ale oyfshriftn zenen geven oyf daytsh

00:04:33.724 --> 00:04:34.646
o-

00:04:35.698 --> 00:04:37.416
LUFSCHUTZ RAUM

00:04:37.416 --> 00:04:39.137
oyf daytsh, PANI, a

00:04:39.137 --> 00:04:41.784
an ort vu me darf zikh farbahaltn

00:04:41.807 --> 00:04:44.571
zenen geven ful di LUFSCHUTZ RAUMEN

00:04:44.571 --> 00:04:46.065
vos hobn gevizn di

00:04:46.065 --> 00:04:48.529
vu me darf zikh farbahaltn in tsayt fun a

00:04:48.529 --> 00:04:49.749
fun a iberfal.

00:04:50.278 --> 00:04:55.017
iz hot men badarft un- un- m'hot badarft farnemen zikh, PANI, es zol aroys

00:04:55.017 --> 00:04:56.246
a prese

00:04:56.286 --> 00:04:57.596
a poylishe.

00:04:57.619 --> 00:05:00.768
m'hot badarft gefinen papir, PANI, tsu drukn

00:05:01.213 --> 00:05:03.530
m'hot badarft ⟨bafinen⟩ ge- e-

00:05:03.530 --> 00:05:05.471
zhurnalistn poylishe

00:05:05.471 --> 00:05:08.044
vos hobn kheyshek, PANI, tsu farnemen zikh

00:05:08.044 --> 00:05:08.829
dermit

00:05:08.829 --> 00:05:10.398
vayle der aynshtel

00:05:10.398 --> 00:05:13.369
fun di poylishe bafelkerung, iber hoypt fun di inteligents

00:05:13.369 --> 00:05:14.845
iz geven a negative

00:05:14.845 --> 00:05:16.496
tsu di frishe regirung.

00:05:17.515 --> 00:05:19.078
yene hobn ⟨gelekhts⟩

00:05:19.084 --> 00:05:20.883
nokh andere UNK, PANI

00:05:20.974 --> 00:05:22.487
mit SIKORSKIn.

00:05:23.927 --> 00:05:27.093
SIKORSKI iz geven di premyer minister fun poylishn

00:05:28.176 --> 00:05:30.839
regirung fun LONDON

00:05:32.095 --> 00:05:34.417
gene- a general, SIKORSKI.

00:05:35.858 --> 00:05:38.670
vos zey ho- zey hobn im aleyn ⟨opgelozt⟩ oykhet.

00:05:39.604 --> 00:05:41.251
er iz geharget gevorn.

00:05:42.777 --> 00:05:46.798
azoy az do hot zikh ongehoybn a

00:05:46.798 --> 00:05:49.503
a sholemdik shoyn in lebn.

00:05:50.016 --> 00:05:51.312
mh

00:05:51.312 --> 00:05:54.949
geven a, a teater. m'hot dos badarft ⟨organirn⟩

00:05:54.949 --> 00:05:57.654
zenen, zenen gekumen tsu forn ACTORn

00:05:57.677 --> 00:05:58.852
poylishe

00:05:58.875 --> 00:06:01.586
un zey hobn zikh mit mir bafrayndet

00:06:01.609 --> 00:06:03.546
un oysgeshtelt pyesen.

00:06:03.546 --> 00:06:05.183
ikh hob bakumen, PANI

00:06:05.183 --> 00:06:07.073
a umtsolike, PANI

00:06:07.073 --> 00:06:10.102
karte, a ayntrit karte

00:06:10.102 --> 00:06:11.289
far bekhinem

00:06:11.295 --> 00:06:12.943
far tsvey perzon

00:06:13.101 --> 00:06:15.469
un m'hot ongehoybn poylishe, PANI

00:06:15.469 --> 00:06:17.719
farshidene UNK pyeses, PANI

00:06:17.725 --> 00:06:19.221
aroystsushteln

00:06:20.408 --> 00:06:23.760
un, un s'iz nokh gevezn demolt

00:06:24.120 --> 00:06:26.510
oykhet a tsayt vos

00:06:26.635 --> 00:06:31.455
vos zibn akht a zeyger hot shoyn keyner nisht getort zayn oyf di gas

00:06:31.478 --> 00:06:33.210
akhuts militer layt

00:06:33.368 --> 00:06:35.927
un ikh hob nisht gegat keyn problemen, PANI

00:06:36.068 --> 00:06:38.239
un ikh fleg geyn ven ikh hob gevolt

00:06:38.413 --> 00:06:40.010
un vu ikh hob gevolt.

00:06:41.940 --> 00:06:43.506
ikh gedenk az ikh hob

00:06:43.506 --> 00:06:47.084
es iz shoyn gevezn e- a radyo, PANI, iz gevezn

00:06:47.084 --> 00:06:48.991
instalirt oyf di gas

00:06:48.991 --> 00:06:51.969
vos hot informirt keseyder vos tut zikh

00:06:51.969 --> 00:06:54.509
un bay dem radyo iz geven fil mentshn

00:06:54.509 --> 00:06:57.679
iz vert geven tsu hern, PANI, vos mentshn shmuesn

00:06:57.820 --> 00:06:58.998
vos tut zikh.

00:06:58.998 --> 00:07:00.631
ikh hob dortn bakent

00:07:00.688 --> 00:07:02.285
davke a meydl.

00:07:02.477 --> 00:07:05.376
ikh hob ir gefregt "vu ken men krign tsigaretn

00:07:05.376 --> 00:07:07.486
tsu koyfn?" ikh hob gereykhert

00:07:07.486 --> 00:07:09.389
iz shoyn nisht geven vu tsu koyfn.

00:07:09.835 --> 00:07:11.753
hot zi mikh arayngenumen

00:07:12.231 --> 00:07:15.060
un zi hot mir gegebn etlekhe peklekh far bekhinem

00:07:15.808 --> 00:07:18.755
un zi hot mir gezogt az ikh vel darfn nokh, vet zi mir gebn

00:07:19.504 --> 00:07:21.694
un zi hot, zi flegt

00:07:21.694 --> 00:07:24.954
dos iz geven in di tsayt ven ikh bin ⟨nokh nokh⟩ geven in shpitol

00:07:24.954 --> 00:07:27.604
un zi fleg kumen tsu mir in shpitol arayn UNK.

00:07:29.950 --> 00:07:34.174
un mit ir bin ikh geven oyf etlekhe teater forshtelungen, ober

00:07:34.174 --> 00:07:35.816
shpeter ayngeladnt

00:07:37.240 --> 00:07:40.198
un azoy hot zikh gedreyt dos lebn, PANI.

00:07:40.198 --> 00:07:42.127
der amt ongehoybn zikh

00:07:42.252 --> 00:07:43.328
UNK tsu

00:07:43.328 --> 00:07:44.788
oystsuvaksn

00:07:44.788 --> 00:07:47.438
dos hobn ongehoybn tsu arbetn dortn a sakh mer

00:07:47.438 --> 00:07:49.083
mentshn. m'hot ongehoybn zikh

00:07:49.083 --> 00:07:50.441
tsu farnemen f-

00:07:50.441 --> 00:07:53.352
mit farkoyfn bikher poylishe

00:07:53.352 --> 00:07:55.470
populere, klasishe

00:07:55.470 --> 00:07:56.944
un geveyntlekhe

00:07:58.350 --> 00:07:59.981
un geveyntlekhe

00:08:02.535 --> 00:08:05.026
azoy az

00:08:05.607 --> 00:08:09.516
s'hot zikh organizirt a normal, a normal lebn

00:08:10.062 --> 00:08:13.552
biz dem nayntn in MAYO

00:08:13.552 --> 00:08:16.097
ven di milkhome hot zikh farendikt

00:08:16.170 --> 00:08:19.691
hot men gemakht a bal dortn oyf di gas.

00:08:19.815 --> 00:08:22.132
an orkester hot g- der, der

00:08:22.132 --> 00:08:25.364
mh der anshtalt gehat an eygenem orkester

00:08:25.364 --> 00:08:27.302
ACTORn, zingers

00:08:27.392 --> 00:08:31.638
un m'hot a gantse nakht geyoyvlt. s'iz geven oyf tish un oyf benk.

00:08:31.864 --> 00:08:33.866
zogt mir, un yidn

00:08:34.412 --> 00:08:37.720
yidn zenen dortn geven, zaynen ongekumen

00:08:36.859 --> 00:08:40.104
dortn zenen keyn mol keyn sakh yidn nisht geven.

00:08:40.104 --> 00:08:42.387
s'hobn gevoynt yidn oyf yene UNK

00:08:42.495 --> 00:08:45.374
UNK groyse shtet vi Poyzn

00:08:46.022 --> 00:08:49.458
i- ober mh d- BYDGOSZCZ

00:08:49.549 --> 00:08:51.782
iz geven yidishe sokhrim

00:08:51.782 --> 00:08:53.863
davke groyse sokhrim

00:08:55.793 --> 00:08:59.195
ober keyn, keyn groyse tsol yidn hobn dortn nisht gevoynt.

00:08:59.117 --> 00:09:01.982
un emetser hot epes gezogt vegn

00:08:59.522 --> 00:09:00.461
di, di

00:09:01.982 --> 00:09:06.232
di situatsye fun yidn itster ven di krig endikt zikh?

00:09:07.183 --> 00:09:10.906
keyn groys mitlayd hobn zey nisht gehat, emes geredt.

00:09:11.672 --> 00:09:14.906
farkert, nisht redndik vegn di vos flegn zogn

00:09:14.980 --> 00:09:18.028
az eyn zakh vos hot gut oyfgetun

00:09:18.085 --> 00:09:22.736
der UNK, der hoypt UNK iz gevezn, er hot gemakht a ordenung mit di yidn.

00:09:24.717 --> 00:09:26.550
ikh fleg oysmaydn

00:09:26.860 --> 00:09:29.402
azelekhe, PANI, sheyn reders

00:09:31.045 --> 00:09:32.929
ober s'iz geven a sakh.

00:09:32.968 --> 00:09:37.248
un es iz, s'iz, UNK dos iz nisht keyn UNK. m'hot farnumen yidishe shtiber

00:09:37.248 --> 00:09:39.078
hobn un guts, PANI

00:09:39.078 --> 00:09:41.720
un di yekes hobn zey gevunen azoy arumet

00:09:41.929 --> 00:09:43.998
me zol zey tsuhelfn, PANI.

00:09:44.072 --> 00:09:45.613
far a fleshl naft

00:09:45.613 --> 00:09:48.555
hot men oysgegebn bahaltene yidn, PANI.

00:09:49.928 --> 00:09:53.179
a, a flash naft hot gekost dortn a por groshn, PANI.

00:09:55.598 --> 00:09:59.962
azoy volt men gekent, PANI, di tsayt fun milkhome

00:10:00.120 --> 00:10:04.147
volt men gekent ⟨farendikn⟩ akhibe ir hot epes UNK.

00:10:04.879 --> 00:10:06.780
ikh hob aykh gevolt fregn

00:10:07.360 --> 00:10:10.425
itst vos di milkhome hot zikh shoyn geendikt

00:10:12.372 --> 00:10:15.420
vos veyst ir fun ayer mishpokhe?

00:10:14.970 --> 00:10:16.128
gornisht.

00:10:16.658 --> 00:10:19.284
ikh bin in Minsk geven etlekhe mol

00:10:19.510 --> 00:10:21.801
vayle tsvey meydlekh

00:10:21.801 --> 00:10:23.520
zenen geblibn lebn

00:10:23.830 --> 00:10:26.271
vos zenen gegangen mit mir in shule arayn

00:10:26.428 --> 00:10:27.834
in onfang shul.

00:10:27.834 --> 00:10:29.527
vi azoy zey hobn zikh

00:10:29.702 --> 00:10:32.244
zey hobn zikh oysbahaltn veys ikh nisht

00:10:32.790 --> 00:10:36.598
iz emes iz az zey zenen geven nisht keyn yidish redndike.

00:10:37.110 --> 00:10:40.445
zey hobn gehat a rizedike bir fabrik

00:10:40.502 --> 00:10:41.879
in Minsk

00:10:43.759 --> 00:10:49.558
un ikh bin geven in Minsk, ⟨zenen⟩ nokh, hot nokh ongehaltn di milkhome

00:10:49.665 --> 00:10:52.379
un ikh bin davke geforn keyn Minsk mit dem

00:10:52.379 --> 00:10:55.329
SIEMKIEWICZn, vayl er hot gegat eltern dortn

00:10:55.352 --> 00:10:57.658
un er hot mikh mitgenumen mit a kotsh

00:10:58.086 --> 00:11:01.067
bin ikh gegangen zen ver iz dortn do.

00:11:01.123 --> 00:11:02.793
ikh hob zikh ongetrofn

00:11:02.793 --> 00:11:06.383
az eyne fun di shvestern iz gezesn i- in kantor.

00:11:07.013 --> 00:11:09.201
m'hot zikh arumgekhapt, PANI

00:11:10.067 --> 00:11:13.959
zi, di mame ire, zenen geven zeyer raykhe mentshn

00:11:13.999 --> 00:11:16.018
un er hot arayngegebn dem binyen

00:11:16.260 --> 00:11:18.349
a tsvey shtokedikn.

00:11:18.349 --> 00:11:21.604
geven a bir fabrik mit a sode vaser fabrik

00:11:23.179 --> 00:11:28.280
un zey hobn zikh geratevet, PANI. ikh hob ir nisht gefregt vu, ven, vos, abi zi lebt

00:11:28.280 --> 00:11:30.280
un zi hot gehat a shvester

00:11:30.280 --> 00:11:31.543
vos iz oyf

00:11:31.583 --> 00:11:33.149
arishe papirn

00:11:33.149 --> 00:11:35.357
geforn oyf arbet keyn Daytshland

00:11:36.240 --> 00:11:38.346
UNK nisht gehat keyn yidishn oyszen

00:11:38.346 --> 00:11:41.516
zi ken, zi hot nisht gekent keyn yidish in gantsn, PANI.

00:11:41.640 --> 00:11:43.355
ir hob ikh gezen a

00:11:43.429 --> 00:11:47.062
a yor shpeter nokh di milkhome bin ikh nokh a mol dortn geforn

00:11:47.062 --> 00:11:50.038
vayl UNK flegt aroyskumen tsuzamen in Varshe

00:11:50.061 --> 00:11:51.860
un es flegt mir oyskumen

00:11:51.867 --> 00:11:55.812
fleg ikh zi aropkhapn dortn, iz gegangen a elektrishe ban

00:11:55.812 --> 00:11:58.509
hot gedoyert tsvontsik minut a for tsu

00:11:58.684 --> 00:12:01.648
fleg ikh geyn zi bazukhn, di shvesters

00:12:01.857 --> 00:12:04.477
di shvesters, un a amolike

00:12:04.477 --> 00:12:05.664
shkheyne oykhet

00:12:05.839 --> 00:12:07.802
a shkheyne mit a tokhter

00:12:07.802 --> 00:12:10.508
mit a yatl vos er iz geven in mayne yorn.

00:12:10.412 --> 00:12:12.498
ir gedenkt zeyer nemen?

00:12:12.522 --> 00:12:13.444
vos?

00:12:13.197 --> 00:12:15.975
ir gedenkt zeyere nemen?

00:12:16.318 --> 00:12:18.033
vi hobn zey geheysn?

00:12:28.890 --> 00:12:30.959
Shoel, Shoel

00:12:31.540 --> 00:12:32.546
Shoel

00:12:33.497 --> 00:12:34.891
HOLTSBAND

00:12:35.691 --> 00:12:37.628
der tate zeyerer hot geheysn

00:12:37.628 --> 00:12:39.583
Shoel HOLTSBAND

00:12:39.775 --> 00:12:42.283
un me flegt im rufn POBYTNIK

00:12:43.251 --> 00:12:46.181
vayl Minsk iz a mol gevezn a, a POBYT

00:12:46.423 --> 00:12:48.883
POBYT shtot. ir veyst nisht vos dos iz?

00:12:48.883 --> 00:12:50.467
a farshikungs

00:12:50.541 --> 00:12:51.457
shtot

00:12:51.457 --> 00:12:54.922
far layt vos hobn zikh oyfgefirt, PANI, nisht azoy

00:12:55.148 --> 00:12:57.386
un vos zey gefeln dos malkhes

00:12:57.645 --> 00:12:58.705
HOLTSBAND

00:12:58.705 --> 00:13:02.021
ober di tsvey shvestern, vos iz vert tsu bamerkn

00:13:02.021 --> 00:13:03.461
hobn zikh geshmadt

00:13:03.788 --> 00:13:05.064
nokh di milkhome.

00:13:05.273 --> 00:13:08.501
zey hobn zikh geshmadt. zey hobn khasene gehat in a kloyster

00:13:08.501 --> 00:13:09.941
mit polyakn

00:13:10.453 --> 00:13:13.926
un zey hobn kinder, PANI, shpor, ikh bin gevezn dortn

00:13:13.926 --> 00:13:16.167
shoyn gevezn gants shpor kinder, PANI

00:13:16.225 --> 00:13:18.446
tsi fi- finef zeks yor

00:13:19.060 --> 00:13:21.433
mit yidishe penemer, PANI

00:13:21.608 --> 00:13:24.082
az m'hot, iz me darf keyn dokument.

00:13:24.628 --> 00:13:28.857
zogt mir, ven ir zent geven in Minsk un in Varshe

00:13:28.881 --> 00:13:33.397
hot ir zikh nokhgefregt vos iz geshen mit ayere eltern?

00:13:32.543 --> 00:13:35.574
bay vemen, vemen i- iz geven nokhtsufregn?

00:13:35.614 --> 00:13:38.409
in Minsk iz nokh geven vemen nokhtsufregn

00:13:38.517 --> 00:13:41.177
UNK nisht geven vemen nokhtsufregn.

00:13:41.571 --> 00:13:44.501
der geto iz geven tsehakt, tsebrokt, PANI

00:13:44.929 --> 00:13:49.507
a, a iny- a binyen vu mir ho'mir gevoynt UNK geven fun fir shtok

00:13:49.507 --> 00:13:50.832
iz geven a kupe

00:13:50.832 --> 00:13:52.618
a kupe, PANI, ash.

00:13:53.333 --> 00:13:56.837
der binyen iz geven in geto, shpeter?

00:13:55.982 --> 00:13:59.806
yo, yo. nisht nor shpeter. frier oykhet geven.

00:14:00.707 --> 00:14:03.300
dos iz geven di grenets take fun geto.

00:14:03.610 --> 00:14:05.426
di gas, di NOWOLIPA.

00:14:05.753 --> 00:14:07.046
zogt mir

00:14:07.137 --> 00:14:12.379
nokhn yor finef un fertsik, ven di milkhome hot zikh geendikt

00:14:13.279 --> 00:14:15.370
mit vos hot ir zikh basheftikt?

00:14:15.220 --> 00:14:18.869
nokh dem, nokh dem farendikn di krig

00:14:18.869 --> 00:14:19.929
hot zikh di

00:14:19.929 --> 00:14:21.749
di, di amt fun

00:14:21.749 --> 00:14:24.984
dem ⟨ministers⟩ UNK informatsye mit propagande

00:14:25.092 --> 00:14:26.672
likvidirt

00:14:26.982 --> 00:14:29.687
un ikh hob zikh ibergetrogn in a shtetl a

00:14:29.687 --> 00:14:32.055
fuftsik kilometer fun Bromberg

00:14:32.061 --> 00:14:33.995
vos heyst TORUN

00:14:34.474 --> 00:14:36.206
Toyrn oyf yidish

00:14:36.516 --> 00:14:38.332
zeyer a sheyn shtetele

00:14:38.710 --> 00:14:41.955
un di gantse tsayt hob ikh biz mayn aroysfor

00:14:41.955 --> 00:14:44.137
hob ikh gevoynt in dem TORUN

00:14:44.582 --> 00:14:48.899
un ikh hob gearbet, PANI, oyf farshidene pletser

00:14:48.899 --> 00:14:50.400
vu ikh bin geven dortn

00:14:50.400 --> 00:14:53.047
a lange tsayt, a shtikl knaker

00:14:54.606 --> 00:14:56.186
in di partey

00:14:56.462 --> 00:14:59.344
un durkh dem hob ikh farnumen, PANI, gants

00:14:59.344 --> 00:15:01.181
nishkoshedike amtn

00:15:02.723 --> 00:15:05.513
⟨nor⟩ getsolt, PANI, hobn zey gants

00:15:05.513 --> 00:15:07.881
gants shlekht.

00:15:07.971 --> 00:15:10.533
s'iz geven arbeter vos zey hobn mer fardint

00:15:10.533 --> 00:15:12.876
fun mir, vos ikh bin geven a direktor.

00:15:13.219 --> 00:15:16.081
ober m'hot gekent, PANI, zhipen

00:15:17.370 --> 00:15:19.249
un emes gezogt hob ikh

00:15:19.249 --> 00:15:22.781
shtark nisht getrakht vegn farlozn Poyln.

00:15:22.804 --> 00:15:24.907
ikh bin gekumen tsu forn

00:15:24.913 --> 00:15:27.556
do aher in dray un zibetsikstn yor

00:15:28.204 --> 00:15:30.307
in a spetsifishe tsayt.

00:15:30.398 --> 00:15:33.665
do hot men mikh ayngeladnt oyf tsvey khasenes,

00:15:34.093 --> 00:15:36.837
der bruder hot khasene gemakht a tokhter

00:15:38.717 --> 00:15:43.672
un a SOBRIN- un di shvester hot khasene gemakht a eynikl

00:15:45.130 --> 00:15:49.815
un zey hobn getsolt, PANI, far dem gantsn gesheft. dos hot gekost a sakh gelt

00:15:50.158 --> 00:15:52.855
UNK zey fregn eyder ikh bin aroysgeforn

00:15:52.855 --> 00:15:56.735
flegn zikh vundern, PANI, tsu velekhe UNK vilstu forn.

00:15:56.735 --> 00:15:59.315
dos hot gekost toyznt tsvey hundert doler

00:15:59.315 --> 00:16:00.415
di rayze.

00:16:00.415 --> 00:16:04.058
in Poyln far aza sume gelt hot men gekent krign, PANI

00:16:04.165 --> 00:16:07.027
a, a gutn kotsh

00:16:07.270 --> 00:16:08.563
a laytishn.

00:16:09.598 --> 00:16:11.482
ober tsugeshpilt

00:16:11.573 --> 00:16:15.330
in mir ot di antisemitishe lage in Poyln.

00:16:15.943 --> 00:16:19.357
s'iz gevorn in Poyln zeyer, zeyer a miese

00:16:19.357 --> 00:16:21.956
a miese zakh. gevezene khaveyrim

00:16:21.956 --> 00:16:25.303
zenen gevorn antisemitn, hobn gehat taynes

00:16:25.596 --> 00:16:29.423
a- az dos vos zeyere poylishe hent hobn geshafn

00:16:29.423 --> 00:16:31.490
viln di yidn umbrengen

00:16:31.490 --> 00:16:34.584
aza yor oyf zey, s'iz UNK emes gevezn.

00:16:35.063 --> 00:16:40.156
yidn hobn ongehaltn az azan sort sotsyalizm vi me boyt ⟨toygn⟩ far di UNK.

00:16:40.156 --> 00:16:41.312
dos iz emes.

00:16:41.312 --> 00:16:43.545
ir hot take nisht UNK

00:16:43.551 --> 00:16:47.224
s'hot derfirt dertsu, PANI, az ⟨zey⟩ zenen untergegangen.

00:16:48.782 --> 00:16:52.083
haynt iz nishto keyn, keyn komunistish Poyln

00:16:53.119 --> 00:16:58.547
afilek WALESA hot tsebrokhn dem kop, PANI, vos er hot, hot tsugezogt goldene gutn

00:16:59.447 --> 00:17:00.841
azoy az

00:17:00.915 --> 00:17:02.411
oyf a moment

00:17:03.227 --> 00:17:05.836
 tsurik keyn Poyln

00:17:07.040 --> 00:17:11.371
ikh hob zikh UNK keyn kheshbn. ikh bin nisht keyn bal ⟨melokhe⟩ fun fakh nisht gevezn

00:17:11.563 --> 00:17:14.935
forn z- mikh hot men gevolt brengen aher

00:17:14.935 --> 00:17:16.721
ober ikh hob nisht gevolt kumen.

00:17:16.727 --> 00:17:19.066
dort bin ikh gevezn emetser.

00:17:19.191 --> 00:17:23.387
do kumen tsu forn darf er hobn toyves, PANI, mit gehilf

00:17:23.477 --> 00:17:25.648
iz shoyn a dervaksener mentsh

00:17:27.443 --> 00:17:30.035
un

00:17:30.700 --> 00:17:34.450
ober di, di lage UNK. ikh hob zikh gerekht aza

00:17:34.450 --> 00:17:37.570
az an ander tog, PANI, vet men mikh meshaleyekh zayn

00:17:38.040 --> 00:17:40.143
un s'vet zayn biter, PANI

00:17:40.285 --> 00:17:42.366
un demolt ken zayn, PANI

00:17:42.366 --> 00:17:45.493
geven a tsayt ven ikh hob afilek gevolt aroysforn

00:17:45.600 --> 00:17:47.416
hot men nisht gevolt aroyslozn

00:17:47.659 --> 00:17:48.752
az ikh n-

00:17:48.752 --> 00:17:52.558
 zey hobn ongehaltn az ikh ⟨soydes veys⟩ a sakh.

00:17:52.558 --> 00:17:54.352
kh'hob take gevust

00:17:55.084 --> 00:17:57.660
un, un m'hot mikh nisht gevolt aroyslozn.

00:17:58.695 --> 00:18:03.667
un do azan gelegnheyt, PANI, ikh for legal un keyner tshepet mikh nisht

00:18:03.775 --> 00:18:06.621
ken mitnemen vos ikh badarf, PANI

00:18:07.200 --> 00:18:08.918
vos ⟨vel ikh zikh⟩, PANI

00:18:08.918 --> 00:18:10.518
oyf di elter, PANI

00:18:11.385 --> 00:18:13.078
un bikhlal

00:18:13.078 --> 00:18:17.018
un, un mayn d- der SOBRINO vos hot getsolt far di rayze

00:18:17.018 --> 00:18:20.458
iz a sh- gut shteyendiker do un hot a band

00:18:20.650 --> 00:18:21.994
a private

00:18:22.135 --> 00:18:27.022
un er hot mir tsugezogt vayl er hot zikh gevolt zayn bavornt un vos UNK im tun.

00:18:27.265 --> 00:18:29.385
er hot mir tsugezogt arbet

00:18:30.623 --> 00:18:35.629
di arbet iz, iz mir nisht gefeln gevorn, PANI, vos er hot mir tsugezogt

00:18:36.225 --> 00:18:39.256
iz shpeter aroysgekumen a boydem derfun

00:18:39.955 --> 00:18:42.176
un tsvishn undz gezogt

00:18:42.655 --> 00:18:45.934
i- hob ikh oykhet groyse taynes, PANI

00:18:45.934 --> 00:18:47.964
tsu yidishe firershaft.

00:18:48.088 --> 00:18:50.438
ikh hob m- do yorn

00:18:50.438 --> 00:18:53.458
bin ikh arum, ongeklapt di tirn fun di kehile

00:18:53.708 --> 00:18:57.921
vayle, v- vi a mentsh, PANI, mit mitl bildung

00:18:58.045 --> 00:19:00.857
i- shraybn ken ikh on grayzn

00:19:01.133 --> 00:19:04.363
m- ikh ken yidish, ikh ken andere leshoynes

00:19:04.363 --> 00:19:08.323
hob ikh gevolt ⟨er⟩ zol ⟨mikh⟩ basheftikn bay zey. ikh hob nisht ⟨gemakht⟩ keyn groyse

00:19:08.323 --> 00:19:09.429
hasoge.

00:19:10.144 --> 00:19:12.537
s'iz geven redt tsu di lomp. s'iz gornisht aroysge⟨kumen⟩.

00:19:12.194 --> 00:19:13.334
zogt mi-

00:19:12.537 --> 00:19:14.408
ober dos iz azoy

00:19:15.460 --> 00:19:17.867
haynt darf men shoyn ⟨hobn a kapore⟩

00:19:17.923 --> 00:19:20.915
ikh hob a ⟨JUBILACIA⟩, PANI. ikh hob fun vos

00:19:20.915 --> 00:19:22.316
fun vos tsu lebn.

00:19:22.316 --> 00:19:25.224
kh'hob a shtark onshpar in Esterke.

00:19:25.720 --> 00:19:27.435
zi iz a goldener mentsh.

00:19:27.525 --> 00:19:28.582
zogt mir

00:19:28.723 --> 00:19:31.265
ven ir kumt keyn Argentine

00:19:31.322 --> 00:19:33.611
in yor dray un zibetsik

00:19:34.410 --> 00:19:35.588
ven ir kumt

00:19:35.588 --> 00:19:37.256
tsu forn keyn Argentine

00:19:36.857 --> 00:19:37.745
yo

00:19:37.785 --> 00:19:40.887
in, vu gefint ir zikh genoy in Poyln?

00:19:40.887 --> 00:19:42.099
in velkher shtot?

00:19:41.903 --> 00:19:45.744
Toyrn, Toyrn. di gantse tsayt shpeter bin ikh geven in Toyrn.

00:19:45.355 --> 00:19:46.425
gut

00:19:46.105 --> 00:19:48.478
in keyn andere shtot hob ikh nisht gevoynt.

00:19:48.090 --> 00:19:53.119
ir hot gehat shverikeytn arayntsukumen keyn Argentine?

00:19:53.445 --> 00:19:58.046
 mit f- frier, mit a por yor frier hob ikh gevolt aleyn kumen

00:19:58.272 --> 00:19:59.830
vayl ikh hob zikh gerekht az

00:19:59.830 --> 00:20:01.458
az zey veln mikh opzogn

00:20:01.458 --> 00:20:04.758
fun farnumene UNK, ikh hob nisht gezen keyn ⟨meglekhkeytn⟩

00:20:04.758 --> 00:20:07.268
vi azoy ikh ken dortn lebn.

00:20:08.042 --> 00:20:10.530
ober dos hot mikh nisht getshepet, PANI.

00:20:11.316 --> 00:20:14.938
zogt mir, ven hot ir zikh bakent mit ayer froy?

00:20:15.282 --> 00:20:17.537
mit, mit Genyen? do.

00:20:17.590 --> 00:20:18.484
ven?

00:20:17.590 --> 00:20:23.420
in dray un zibetsikstn yor, PANI, in e- in ershtn khoydesh fun mayn kumen

00:20:23.420 --> 00:20:26.946
hot mikh mayn bruder avekgefirt tsu di shayres hapleyte

00:20:27.195 --> 00:20:31.543
un do hob ikh gefinen a bakantn vos ⟨mir ze'mir⟩ geven in Sibir

00:20:31.937 --> 00:20:33.078
tsuzamen.

00:20:33.810 --> 00:20:36.557
in ershtn moment hot zikh mir gedakht nor

00:20:36.557 --> 00:20:41.583
ober ikh hob im opgeshtelt un gefregt "bist gevezn do un do?" "yo."

00:20:41.792 --> 00:20:46.612
un ikh hob im gezogt dem nomen maynem. "ah, ⟨ikh volt⟩ dir nisht derkent."

00:20:46.180 --> 00:20:47.895
vi, vi heyst er?

00:20:54.010 --> 00:20:55.846
falt aroys fun zikorn.

00:20:55.020 --> 00:20:56.770
zogt mir

00:20:55.846 --> 00:20:57.294
er iz do. er lebt

00:20:57.317 --> 00:20:58.897
un, un, un, un

00:20:59.376 --> 00:21:01.929
ikh hob nokh demolt nisht geredt keyn yidish.

00:21:01.929 --> 00:21:03.723
ikh hob do geredt poylish.

00:21:04.118 --> 00:21:05.836
s'iz mir geven shver tsu redn

00:21:05.836 --> 00:21:09.882
yidish. shtelt zikh for, draysik yor tsayt hob ikh nisht geredt keyn yidish.

00:21:11.357 --> 00:21:12.329
un

00:21:12.302 --> 00:21:15.299
zogt mir dem nomen fun ayer froy.

00:21:15.475 --> 00:21:18.422
Genye REZNIK

00:21:18.630 --> 00:21:19.872
POPOWSKI.

00:21:20.841 --> 00:21:21.982
dos iz zi.

00:21:23.035 --> 00:21:27.534
un zi iz gevezn a kultur tuerin in dem sh- farband

00:21:28.283 --> 00:21:31.533
iz di shvester mayne iz demolt gevezn

00:21:31.533 --> 00:21:34.003
un der bruder vos zey hobn mikh aropgefirt

00:21:34.003 --> 00:21:37.349
dortn, un ikh hob zi bakent UNK. m'hot geshmuest, PANI

00:21:37.349 --> 00:21:38.509
vi geveyntlekh

00:21:38.509 --> 00:21:40.989
un mayn shvester hot ir gekent

00:21:40.989 --> 00:21:43.374
vayl zi hot lib ⟨gegat⟩ tsu geyn oyf ire

00:21:43.374 --> 00:21:45.151
oyf ire lektsyes

00:21:45.681 --> 00:21:49.337
un zi hot gevust az zi iz a poylish kenerin.

00:21:49.410 --> 00:21:55.040
iz zi hot ir oysgezukht bald dortn in dem farband un hot tsugeleygt un ir forgeshtelt.

00:21:55.114 --> 00:21:57.166
dos iz Genye, PANI

00:21:57.223 --> 00:22:00.119
ahin un aher. azoy hobn mir zikh bakent

00:22:01.476 --> 00:22:05.008
un ikh bin nokh etlekhe mol dortn gegangen

00:22:05.008 --> 00:22:07.832
in dem farband arayn. m'hot zikh bakent.

00:22:08.158 --> 00:22:10.588
un m'hot gekhapt a shmues, PANI

00:22:10.588 --> 00:22:13.368
vi zi hot gehert az ikh hob farlozt Poyln

00:22:13.368 --> 00:22:15.628
bin ikh geforn durkh Sokolov UNK

00:22:15.718 --> 00:22:18.496
a gantse b- a gantse, PANI

00:22:19.009 --> 00:22:21.905
metsie, PANI, vayl dos iz geven ir shtot.

00:22:22.553 --> 00:22:24.617
un, ober azoy a

00:22:24.617 --> 00:22:29.499
a por vokhn zikh ge- kimat yedn tog getrofn, geshmuest

00:22:29.522 --> 00:22:32.351
ahin un aher vegn farshidene zakhn

00:22:32.509 --> 00:22:35.788
un, ikh zol aykh nisht zogn keyn lignt

00:22:35.788 --> 00:22:38.342
hot zi aleyn mir forgeshlogn

00:22:38.871 --> 00:22:41.059
tsi ikh volt nisht gevolt blaybn do.

00:22:42.803 --> 00:22:45.345
oh, dos iz geven far mir a UNK

00:22:46.431 --> 00:22:47.491
vayle

00:22:47.491 --> 00:22:50.660
ikh bin shoyn tsvishn tsayt gevezn do in shtub bayn ir.

00:22:50.886 --> 00:22:52.601
kh'hob gezen zi hot a shtub.

00:22:53.620 --> 00:22:55.183
zi arbet

00:22:55.324 --> 00:22:58.575
un zi fleg krign a por toler fun di yekes

00:22:59.087 --> 00:23:00.583
a por dolarn

00:23:01.045 --> 00:23:04.450
an ⟨onshpar⟩ UNK. do iz, vu nisht, vos es zol nisht zayn

00:23:04.450 --> 00:23:06.084
umkumen ken ikh nisht.

00:23:06.343 --> 00:23:09.172
zi hot tsvey tekhter, tsvey eydems

00:23:09.752 --> 00:23:12.125
un ikh bin arayngegangen ⟨nokh⟩ dem.

00:23:13.127 --> 00:23:14.724
bin arayngegangen.

00:23:14.916 --> 00:23:17.762
in a khoydesh arum hobn mir khasene gehat.

00:23:19.962 --> 00:23:21.356
un ikh ho- i-

00:23:20.150 --> 00:23:22.432
